  "3194390": {
    "name": "勘洞联盟",
    "steam_appid": 3194390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/fcb9df4580925d4d206d9550004097d1.webp?t=1771996314\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/fcb9df4580925d4d206d9550004097d1.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=88 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是在一个充满各种动物势力和怪物的地洞里冒险的平台跳跃肉鸽游戏，包含平台跳跃、多种多样的武器和能力、boss战斗、角色收集。死亡不是终点，在一次次的挑战后，你或许会逐渐知晓这个怪异世界表象下的暗流涌动……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/507ed73e0db566bec900c3f8070a2a65.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" width=680 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/507ed73e0db566bec900c3f8070a2a65.webm?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/507ed73e0db566bec900c3f8070a2a65.mp4?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/fb0a43f62a77aef9c11bd8b20c96595a.webp?t=1771996314\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/fb0a43f62a77aef9c11bd8b20c96595a.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=88 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个地下洞穴中，你能找到许多种武器供你使用：自动手枪，猎枪，大炮，巨斧，大剑，匕首，魔杖，法杖……甚至是——一根巨大的胡萝卜？！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/53de0fdc98b162f1ba94ac4fb46c9d96.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" width=680 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/53de0fdc98b162f1ba94ac4fb46c9d96.webm?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/53de0fdc98b162f1ba94ac4fb46c9d96.mp4?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/7698a1bed57d230c2dd3e615e1c52081.webp?t=1771996314\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/7698a1bed57d230c2dd3e615e1c52081.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=88 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下……非常深！这里有着各种不同的生态坏境和地形，同时也栖息着各种强大的怪物和各方势力。他们面对唐突出现的你——一个觊觎财宝和秘密的冒险者，可不会轻易地让你通过。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/8a1393cdf2b82f560a206d2b47203637.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" width=680 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/8a1393cdf2b82f560a206d2b47203637.webm?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/8a1393cdf2b82f560a206d2b47203637.mp4?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/2c067d2f7c1f2e9183b4c2c08e85aaf8.webp?t=1771996314\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/2c067d2f7c1f2e9183b4c2c08e85aaf8.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=88 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收益和风险是并存的！地洞里有许许多多强大的能力和宝箱中的财宝等着你去发现！(当然还有秘密）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/ef6bcac4a77035e41ca3c7329a559763.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" width=680 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/ef6bcac4a77035e41ca3c7329a559763.webm?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/ef6bcac4a77035e41ca3c7329a559763.mp4?t=1771996314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/4b971b680fbb67f813e5291bcbbde30c.webp?t=1771996314\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194390/extras/4b971b680fbb67f813e5291bcbbde30c.poster.avif?t=1771996314\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=88 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拥有上百种不同的武器，不同种类的武器都有着独特的天赋倾向，尝试新的武器，配合天赋点与能力加成，让这些武器在战斗中变得更趁手！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>近百种不同的能力加成，各具特色。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>担心一直拿不到趁手的武器和强力的能力？没关系！天赋点系统会弥补这一点！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>天赋点歪了……？额，接下来或许还能拿到强力的道具组合与适合你天赋的武器的，祝你好运！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个有多种“动物”阵营的世界：犬、猫、兔、甚至老鼠。他们各怀鬼胎，深入地下，发掘财宝、探寻真相。</strong></p></li></ul>",
